 {\"ngram\": \"- Dark\", \"from\": 173, \"to\": 179}, {\"ngram\": \"Horses\", \"from\": 180, \"to\": 186}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports advertising world\", \"from\": 190, \"to\": 218}, {\"ngram\": \"its breath\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 247}, {\"ngram\": \"the highs\", \"from\": 254, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"lows\", \"from\": 268, \"to\": 272}, {\"ngram\": \"the Euros\", \"from\": 276, \"to\": 285}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 287, \"to\": 299}, {\"ngram\": \"Paralympics\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 315}, {\"ngram\": \"other ideas\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best athletes\", \"from\": 360, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest brands\", \"from\": 390, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"a month\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 428}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting excellence\", \"from\": 432, \"to\": 451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whilst every brand and his dog tried to tap into authentic fan insights during the Euros, it's the athletes and their stories that take centre stage in the work adorning the City of Lights.\", \"from\": 456, \"to\": 645, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every brand\", \"from\": 463, \"to\": 474}, {\"ngram\": \"his dog\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 486}, {\"ngram\": \"authentic fan insights\", \"from\": 505, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"the Euros\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 563}, {\"ngram\": \"their stories\", \"from\": 568, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"centre stage\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 604}, {\"ngram\": \"the work\", \"from\": 608, \"to\": 616}, {\"ngram\": \"the City\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 634}, {\"ngram\": \"Lights\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 644}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Channel 4's work for the Paralympic Games is becoming a bit of a moment in the advertising calendar, perhaps not yet on the scale of John Lewis Christmas, but it's consistently brilliant and boundary pushing.\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 855, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 647, \"end\": 656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.295002064726938e-12, \"text\": \"Channel 4\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4\"}, {\"begin\": 780, \"end\": 790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lewis_Partnership\", \"score\": 0.9951859275737537, \"rank\": 0.004837359826732829, \"text\": \"John Lewis\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lewis_Partnership\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Lewis_Partnership\"}, {\"begin\": 791, \"end\": 800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christmas\", \"score\": 0.9777221791469655, \"rank\": 0.022785428718331058, \"text\": \"Christmas\", \"types\": [\"Q1445650\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christmas\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christmas\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paralympic Games\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 688}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 701, \"to\": 706}, {\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 718}, {\"ngram\": \"the advertising calendar\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"the scale\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 776}, {\"ngram\": \"consistently brilliant and boundary pushing\", \"from\": 811, \"to\": 854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This year feels like a punch in the gut compared to the more joyful work of Olympics past, but it's potentially even more affecting.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 988, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This year\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"a punch\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"the gut\", \"from\": 888, \"to\": 895}, {\"ngram\": \"the more joyful work\", \"from\": 908, \"to\": 928}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"even more affecting\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 987}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The writing is superb, 'it's keeping your skin as a souvenir' just one example of an ad littered with great lines.\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1104, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The writing\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"your skin\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"a souvenir' just one example\", \"from\": 1040, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"an ad\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1077}, {\"ngram\": \"great lines\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1103}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The hypnotic sound design and repetitive cuts keeps the audience hooked, as we see the intensity, strength and superhuman ability of the athletes.\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The hypnotic sound design\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1131}, {\"ngram\": \"repetitive cuts\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"the audience\", \"from\": 1158, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"the intensity\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1212}, {\"ngram\": \"superhuman ability\", \"from\": 1217, \"to\": 1235}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1251}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City AM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"The Turnover\", \"from\": 1276, \"to\": 1288}, {\"ngram\": \"your weekly roundup\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"sport business news\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1332}, {\"ngram\": \"analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1379}, {\"ngram\": \"City AM's sports desk\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1406}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whilst the idea of sport bringing people together, even fishermen during a storm, is not the most original thought, I do feel less cynical about advertising like this post Covid-19.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\"