wish our athletes good luck or tell us they are their biggest supporters, (have a point of view for goodness sake) but I can not be too harsh on Kevin the Carrot.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2114, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a fan\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1914}, {\"ngram\": \"brands\", \"from\": 1918, \"to\": 1924}, {\"ngram\": \"adverts\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1948}, {\"ngram\": \"our athletes\", \"from\": 1957, \"to\": 1969}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1988, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"their biggest supporters\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2024}, {\"ngram\": \"a point\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2039}, {\"ngram\": \"view\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2047}, {\"ngram\": \"goodness sake\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"Kevin\", \"from\": 2097, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"the Carrot\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aldi's orange mascot is a firm favourite with my toddlers, especially when he makes underpants puns.\", \"from\": 2116, \"to\": 2216, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2116, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Aldi\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Aldi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my toddlers\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"underpants puns\", \"from\": 2200, \"to\": 2215}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This has all the hallmarks of an advert made by a very large committee.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2289, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the hallmarks\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"an advert\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2257}, {\"ngram\": \"a very large committee\", \"from\": 2266, \"to\": 2288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have watched it five times and I still can not tell you exactly what the message is.\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"exactly what\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2360}, {\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 2361, \"to\": 2372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Level Up Your Game\\\" is not only very generic, it feels like a brand trying to be down with the kids but using stock footage to do it.\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2512, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Level\", \"from\": 2379, \"to\": 2384}, {\"ngram\": \"Your Game\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2397}, {\"ngram\": \"a brand\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"the kids\", \"from\": 2470, \"to\": 2478}, {\"ngram\": \"stock footage\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2502}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Strategically I really like this ad, it's reminding me that I can have a guilt free flutter on the lottery and some of my losses will help support British athletes, win win - or, more likely, lose win.\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2715, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2661, \"end\": 2668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9490299080832296, \"rank\": 0.053699652422857874, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this ad\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2549}, {\"ngram\": \"a guilt free flutter\", \"from\": 2585, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"the lottery\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2620}, {\"ngram\": \"my losses\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2642}, {\"ngram\": \"win\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some charming vignettes and interesting match cuts leave for a nice little spot.\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2797, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some charming vignettes\", \"from\": 2717, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"interesting match cuts\", \"from\": 2745, \"to\": 2767}, {\"ngram\": \"a nice little spot\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2796}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC raised the bar in craft with its Tokyo 2020 advert, so this film had big shoes to fill for Paris 2024.\", \"from\": 2799, \"to\": 2909, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2803, \"end\": 2806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9985369358006588, \"rank\": 0.0014637817759457798, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 2840, \"end\": 2845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9986198873465072, \"rank\": 0.001382016779436401, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2898, \"end\": 2908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.999999999402462, \"rank\": 5.976920516774031e-10, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the bar\", \"from\": 2814, \"to\": 2821}, {\"ngram\": \"craft\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2830}, {\"ngram\": \"this film\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2871}, {\"ngram\": \"big shoes\", \"from\": 2876, \"to\": 2885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going all in on The City of Love is brave, as I am sure other brands might play in the same area, but this beautiful animation really hits the chord emotionally.\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 3072, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The City\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"Love\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2943}, {\"ngram\": \"other brands\", \"from\": 2967, \"to\": 2979}, {\"ngram\": \"the same area\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3007}, {\"ngram\": \"this beautiful animation\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"the chord\", \"from\": 3050, \"to\": 3059}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The music choice could have been cliched, but paired with the well written VO it really works.\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3168, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The music choice\", \"from\": 3074, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"the well written VO\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3151}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This ad packs a punch and builds to an impressive crescendo, but I can not help notice it's attempt to riff on Nike's 'You Can not Stop Us' film, which was a masterclass in editing athletes together from different worlds.\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3391, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3281, \"end\": 3285, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"score\": 0.9982870120037655, \"rank\": 0.0017156831605727029, \"text\": \"Nike\", \"types\": [\"Q728\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/MIM-3_Nike_Ajax\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This ad\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3177}, {\"ngram\": \"a punch\", \"from\": 3184, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"an impressive crescendo\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"attempt\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3269}, {\"ngram\": \"Us' film\", \"from\": 3306, \"to\": 3314}, {\"ngram\": \"a masterclass\", \"from\": 3326, \"to\": 3339}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3359}, {\"ngram\": \"different worlds\", \"from\": 3374, \"to\": 3390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Using that technique for an ad like this feels a bit forced to me.\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that technique\", \"from\": 3399, \"to\": 3413}, {\"ngram\": \"an ad\", \"from\": 3418, \"to\": 3423}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Adam Burns is the Creative Director atDark Horses.\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3511, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Adam Burns\", \"from\": 3461, \"to\": 3471}, {\"ngram\": \"the Creative Director atDark Horses\", \"from\": 3475, \"to\": 3510}]}, {